How To Install Google Chrome, Selenium & Chromedriver For AWS EC2 Instances
    Download Chrome, this should give you the latest stable version.

        wget https://dl.google.com/linux/direct/google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
        sudo apt install ./google-chrome-stable_current_amd64.deb
        google-chrome-stable --version

    If you are using Chrome version 100, please download ChromeDriver 100.0.4896.60
        sudo wget https://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/100.0.4896.60/chromedriver_linux64.zip
        sudo unzip chromedriver_linux64.zip
        sudo mv chromedriver /usr/bin/chromedriver
        chromedriver --version

    Make sure your chrome version and driver version are matching